{
  "stem": "15686.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before then, you could go to anyone that you wanted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then the Nazis restricted that and said only one or two are open to Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I remember my brother and I having to take the subway to go to this particular pool where we had swimming lessons.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the instructor was a Jewish physical ed teacher, whom we knew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all his students were the Jewish kids.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were other instructors there from other schools, but they were all Gentile.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So never the twain mixed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, we did our thing, they did there's in the same pool, but we didn't talk to each other.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that sort of went on for a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then the government decided that Jews were not entitled to go to any swimming pool, and that cut that short, and that was about I'd say 1938.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I mentioned earlier, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] both my parents liked music very much.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was an amateur opera singer, and he was active in the-- what they called a Kulturbund, which was a culture-- a cultural organization sponsored by the Jewish community of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they would put on operas and plays and what have you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He also sang as a Cantor on the holidays, not because he needed to make money, but he loved to sing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother played the piano.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My father would sing in the shower, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we heard him, and he would-- when friends come over, they would ask him to sing, and he would sing an aria from some opera.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And ever since I was a little boy, I remember him singing, and there was music.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
